[normal]tment in growth relies 
[normal]on a stro
[normal]nger relationship between risk and reward for cities, allowing them to share in the dividends of growth.  Fiscal reform will achieve this, but also needs to be linked to a wider reform of the public sector in order to have maximum impact.  
